name: #2 - Perspectives of Collab
description:
This work was made on a crazy trip! This digitized analog collage work is part of a series on collage techniques based on the neoconcrete, futuristic cyberpunk style.  
The mystery of the eye is also present in this work. The pixels and lines that connect everything to the plus give the idea of the value of collab today.

- Kejo, Brazil.
